latestPosts.caption:
Such a pleasure to be a part of the creative team behind the iconic ‘Kalki x Raja Kumari’ Campaign.

What started months ago with moodboards and long conversations about silhouettes, textures, and drapes slowly blossomed into something truly magical. The incredibly talented design team at Kalki poured their hearts into every sketch and swatch, while Raja brought her attention to detail and intention to every piece, making sure it celebrates every kind of woman. As the Stylist and Creative Director, it’s been a milestone moment for me, my first time leading a campaign of this scale for a brand I deeply admire @kalkifashion . Sending big love to my bestie and favourite client @therajakumari - Thank you for trusting me with this project. I’m truly grateful for this experience and heart is full. ✨
